05:29.660 --> 05:31.200
BENNETT,
YOU ALWAYS DO THIS.

05:31.230 --> 05:32.730
HONEY, LOOK AT HER.

05:32.770 --> 05:34.300
YEAH, I SEE HER.

05:34.330 --> 05:36.100
WELL?

05:36.140 --> 05:38.270
WE HAD TO DEAL WITH
