THROUGH THAT AGAIN.

05:39.840 --> 05:42.140
SO, I'M JUST SUPPOSED
TO LEAVE HER OUT THERE?

05:42.180 --> 05:44.010
WE HAVE A TRUCK TO UNLOAD.
COME ON.

05:44.040 --> 05:51.520
