06:30.520 --> 06:32.860
UM, UH,
NOT MY PLACE TO SAY.

06:33.830 --> 06:35.760
I MEAN,
SHE DOESN'T HAVE ME.

06:35.800 --> 06:37.860
I KNOW YOU LOVE ALEX.

06:37.900 --> 06:39.930
I'VE KNOWN YOU TWO
FOR A LONG TIME.

06:39.970 --> 06:41.930
YEAH, I KNOW.

06:41.970 --> 06:44.400
