I CAN UNDERSTAND WHY.

06:49.810 --> 06:51.280
BUT WHAT I MEAN
IS HELP FOR YOU.

06:51.310 --> 06:54.180
BRAD, THIS IS A LOT OF PAIN
AND HURT YOU'RE DEALING WITH.

06:54.210 --> 06:55.850
I'M FINE.

06:55.880 --> 06:57.680
WELL,
I DON'T THINK YOU ARE.

06:59.150 --> 07:00.550
IF YOU SEE MARCIE,
CAN YOU JUST TELL HER

07:00.590 --> 07:02.390
THAT I'M LOOKING FOR HER?

07:02.420 --> 07:04.390
YES...YES, I WILL.

07:04.420 --> 07:05.760
THANK YOU.

07:05.790 --> 07:08.330
[ INDISTINCT ANNOUNCEMENT
OVER P.A. ]

07:10.500 --> 07:12.230
