<i> HI, THIS IS MARCIE.</i>
<i> LEAVE A MESSAGE.</i>

07:16.270 --> 07:17.970
MARCIE, IT'S BRAD.

07:18.000 --> 07:19.900
I'VE BEEN LOOKING
EVERYWHERE FOR YOU.

07:19.940 --> 07:21.140
