YOU SURE YOU DON'T
WANT THIS NUMBER?

21:34.360 --> 21:35.990
OKAY, THANKS.

21:36.030 --> 21:37.590
TAKE CARE OF YOURSELF.

21:37.630 --> 21:42.270
♪♪

21:42.300 --> 21:43.700
BRAD?

21:45.400 --> 21:46.940
WHAT ARE YOU DOING HERE?

21:46.970 --> 21:48.740
WHAT ARE<i> YOU</i> DOING HERE?

21:48.770 --> 21:51.640
WHAT WAS THAT ALL ABOUT?
HUH?

21:51.680 --> 21:53.440
DID YOU GET A SHOT?
WHAT?

21:53.480 --> 21:54.680
I KNEW THAT BITCH
WAS GONNA BURN YOU.

21:54.710 --> 21:56.050
I JUST KNEW IT WAS
A MATTER OF TIME.

21:56.080 --> 21:57.050
WHAT ARE YOU TALKING
ABOUT, EDDIE?

21:57.080 --> 21:58.320
I'M TALKING ABOUT
YOUR WIFE -- ALEX --

21:58.350 --> 22:00.550
WHO'S BEEN WHORING AROUND
WITH EVERYBODY.

22:00.590 --> 22:02.320
YOU UP HERE GETTING A SHOT?
I'M NOT DOING THIS.

22:02.350 --> 22:05.120
NO, BRAD, WHAT ARE YOU
DOING HERE? TELL ME.

22:05.160 --> 22:06.620
I DON'T WANT TO
TALK ABOUT IT, OKAY?

22:06.660 --> 22:08.630
OKAY, OKAY.

22:08.660 --> 22:10.130
LOOK, MAN, I'M JUST TRYING TO
FIGURE OUT WHAT'S HAPPENING.

22:10.160 --> 22:12.860
WANT TO GO GRAB SOME BEERS
LATER ON TONIGHT AND CATCH UP?

22:12.900 --> 22:15.100
I'M NOT GONNA BE THERE.

22:15.130 --> 22:17.000
WHAT IS IT?

22:17.040 --> 22:18.870
WHAT'S THIS ABOUT, MAN,
YOUR CREDIT CARD OR WHAT?

22:18.900 --> 22:20.870
I'LL PAY YOU BACK.
YEAH, I KNOW YOU WILL.

22:20.910 --> 22:22.710
YOU ARE GONNA PAY ME BACK.
I KNOW THAT.

22:22.740 --> 22:24.070
OKAY. LOOK,
JUST SETTLE DOWN.

22:24.110 --> 22:25.710
AND I'LL SEE YOU
AT THE HOUSE TONIGHT.

22:25.740 --> 22:28.250
I'LL BE AT YOUR PLACE AT 8:00.
AND IF I'M NOT THERE,
I'LL BE IN THE BACKYARD.

22:28.280 --> 22:30.110
I'M NOT GONNA BE THERE,
I SAID.

22:30.150 --> 22:31.210
WHY NOT?
WHERE ARE YOU GONNA BE?

22:31.250 --> 22:33.980
BECAUSE I'M DONE
WITH ALEX.

22:34.020 --> 22:35.720
DONE DONE?

22:35.750 --> 22:37.690
NEED HELP GETTING
RID OF THAT BODY?

22:37.720 --> 22:39.360
I'M NOT GONNA KILL HER,
YOU IDIOT.

22:39.390 --> 22:41.530
WELL, IF SHE'S NOT IN A BOX,
THEN YOU AIN'T DONE WITH HER.
THAT'S THE PROBLEM.

22:41.560 --> 22:43.060
SEE, THIS IS EXACTLY WHY
I CAN'T TALK TO YOU.

22:43.100 --> 22:45.130
NO, NO, NO, NO, NO.
BUT LISTEN. I'M -- I'M SORRY.

22:45.160 --> 22:46.230
THAT'S WHAT NEEDS TO
HAPPEN WITH HER.

22:46.270 --> 22:49.100
BUT I'M JUST HAPPY TO
FINALLY HEAR YOU SAY

22:49.130 --> 22:51.370
THAT YOU'RE DONE,
FINALLY.

22:51.400 --> 22:55.170
I AM. I'M FINALLY DONE,
AND IT FEELS GOOD.

22:55.210 --> 22:57.510
WHAT DID SHE DO?

22:57.540 --> 22:59.080
WHAT<i> DIDN'T</i> SHE DO?

22:59.110 --> 23:00.540
[ SCOFFS ] RIGHT?

23:00.580 --> 23:02.210
SHE LIED TO ME
ABOUT THE DNA.

23:02.250 --> 23:03.750
WAIT, WHAT?
AND THEN SHE TOLD ME

23:03.780 --> 23:05.580
THAT DOCTOR RASTON
SWITCHED THE DNA RESULTS,

23:05.620 --> 23:06.880
WHICH IS ANOTHER
COMPLETE AND UTTER LIE.

23:06.920 --> 23:08.520
SO SHE DID NOT?

23:08.550 --> 23:09.890
NO.

23:09.920 --> 23:12.160
AND YOU CAUGHT HER
IN THE LIE?

23:12.190 --> 23:14.120
YOU COULD CALL IT THAT.

23:14.160 --> 23:17.090
THAT'S COUNT ONE, BRAD.
SO, WHAT'S NEXT?

23:17.130 --> 23:18.800
HUH? WHOSE BABY IS IT?

23:18.830 --> 23:19.730
I DON'T KNOW.

23:19.770 --> 23:21.770
IF IT'S NOT RANDAL'S,
IS IT LUSHION'S?

23:21.800 --> 23:23.400
I DON'T THINK
IT'S LUSHION'S.

23:23.440 --> 23:25.300
COME ON, HOMIE.
YOU GOTTA KNOW SOMETHING.

23:25.340 --> 23:26.500
I DON'T.

23:26.540 --> 23:27.900
LOOK, I KNOW YOU'RE GOING
THROUGH A LOT, MAN.

23:27.940 --> 23:30.270
LET ME TAKE CARE OF THIS.
LET ME GET THESE ANSWERS
FOR YOU, OKAY?

23:30.310 --> 23:31.640
I PROMISE I'LL GET
TO THE BOTTOM OF IT.

23:31.680 --> 23:33.480
AND HOW ARE YOU
GONNA DO THAT?

23:33.510 --> 23:36.110
DON'T ASK ME THAT. YOU KNOW
EDDIE'S GOT HIS WAYS.

23:36.150 --> 23:37.250
I DON'T CARE, EDDIE.

23:37.280 --> 23:39.320
YOU KNOW, YOU -- YOU DO WHATEVER
YOU NEED TO DO, OKAY?

23:39.350 --> 23:40.650
THANK YOU, FOR ONCE.

23:40.690 --> 23:42.720
LET ME DO WHAT I DO
AND HELP YOU OUT.

23:42.750 --> 23:46.090
IN FACT, SCRATCH THAT.
I DON'T WANT YOU TO DO ANYTHING.

23:46.130 --> 23:47.420
WHY?
WHY DO YOU GIVE A SHIT?

23:47.460 --> 23:49.560
NO, BECAUSE I CARE ABOUT
MY KIDS, AND I KNOW
HOW YOU'RE GONNA BE.

23:49.600 --> 23:52.330
YOUR KIDS ARE YOUNG, BRAD.
THEY NEED TO LEARN THAT
DEATH IS A PART OF LIFE

23:52.360 --> 23:54.400
AND THEIR MOM IS A WHORE,
PERIOD.

23:54.430 --> 23:55.870
I CAN'T --
I-I CAN'T DO THIS, EDDIE.

23:55.900 --> 23:58.170
OKAY,, LOOK, I'M JUST SO TIRED
OF HER LYING TO YOU

23:58.200 --> 24:01.070
OVER AND OVER AGAIN, BRAD.

24:01.110 --> 24:02.640
I MEAN, ALEX AND I GREW UP
TOGETHER AS COUSINS.

24:02.670 --> 24:05.010
SHE WAS RAISED A CHRISTIAN.
SHE HAS LOST HER WALK WITH GOD.

24:05.040 --> 24:06.510
I NEED TO GO OVER THERE
AND PRAY WITH HER.

24:06.550 --> 24:08.610
I'M GOING TO YOUR HOUSE TONIGHT
TO TALK TO HER DIRECTLY.

24:08.650 --> 24:10.050
I'M NOT GONNA BE THERE.

24:10.080 --> 24:11.050
WELL, I'M GONNA GO THERE.

24:11.080 --> 24:13.150
I'M GONNA PRAY WITH HER
WITH MY PRIEST.

24:13.190 --> 24:14.180
SO I'D HOPE YOU'D COME.

24:14.220 --> 24:15.390
YOU TWO HAVE FUN.

24:15.420 --> 24:16.490
WHERE YOU GONNA BE?

24:16.520 --> 24:18.290
I'LL COME OVER THERE
AND CRASH.

24:18.320 --> 24:19.420
BYE, EDDIE.

24:19.460 --> 24:20.620
HEY, YOU KNOW I CAN TRACK YOU,
RIGHT?

24:20.660 --> 24:24.230
ALL RIGHT,
I'LL SEE YOU TONIGHT.

24:24.260 --> 24:26.260
SLUT.

24:30.570 --> 24:34.440
♪♪

24:34.470 --> 24:36.540
WELL, HELLO.

24:36.580 --> 24:39.010
♪♪

24:39.040 --> 24:42.610
OFFICER WILLIS.

24:42.650 --> 24:44.610
I SEE YOU'RE UP
AND AROUND.

24:44.650 --> 24:47.880
YEAH, WELL YOU KNOW
I HAD TO GET TO WORK.

24:47.920 --> 24:50.050
SO YOU'RE DOING
YOUR MAKE UP?

24:50.090 --> 24:52.920
INDEED.

24:52.960 --> 24:54.930
FIGURED A GIRL LIKE YOU
WOULD HAVE A STYLIST

24:54.960 --> 24:57.660
AND A GLAM SQUAD.

24:57.700 --> 24:59.960
NO, I ACTUALLY GAVE THEM
THE DAY OFF.

25:00.000 --> 25:02.170
SO YOU JUST WALK AROUND
WITH A LITTLE COMPACT

25:02.200 --> 25:04.300
IN YOUR PURSE, HUH?

25:04.340 --> 25:05.640
YEAH, WELL YOU KNOW
IT'S AN OLD TRICK

25:05.670 --> 25:08.640
MY WIFE TAUGHT ME TO
COVER THE BRUISES.

25:08.670 --> 25:11.710
OH WELL, YOU ARE DOING
THAT FOUNDATION, GIRL.

25:11.740 --> 25:12.980
YOU DOING IT!

25:13.010 --> 25:14.480
YES!

25:14.510 --> 25:16.750
WHY, THANK YOU.

25:16.780 --> 25:19.750
THIS WIFE OF YOURS, MITCH.

25:19.790 --> 25:23.090
YOU TALK ABOUT HER A LOT,
BUT I NEVER MET HER.

25:23.120 --> 25:25.120
NO, AND, UH, YOU WON'T.

25:25.160 --> 25:26.320
I WOULDN'T SAY
I NEVER SEEN HER.

25:26.360 --> 25:29.030
I'VE SEEN HER
PLENTY OF TIMES.

25:29.060 --> 25:31.230
I'VE NEVER MET HER.

25:31.260 --> 25:33.800
SO WHAT, YOU STALKING
MY WIFE NOW, HUH?

25:33.830 --> 25:36.570
OH, I'M STALKING EVERYTHING
ABOUT YOUR PATHETIC-ASS LIFE.

25:36.600 --> 25:40.100
HMM, YOU KNOW I HATE
WHEN THAT HAPPENS.

25:40.140 --> 25:42.140
YEAH, WHY IS THAT?

25:42.170 --> 25:44.870
BECAUSE I DATED GUYS LIKE
YOU BEFORE, IN THE PAST.

25:44.910 --> 25:48.480
YOU ALL END UP CRAZY,
POSSESSIVE, AND DOMINEERING.

25:48.510 --> 25:50.450
I'M JUST GONNA LEAVE YOU
RIGHT HERE UNTIL I FEEL BETTER.

25:50.480 --> 25:52.380
C'MON MAN,
YOU'VE HAD YOUR FUN.

25:52.420 --> 25:54.250
NOW STOP,
ENOUGH IS ENOUGH.

25:54.290 --> 25:56.220
FIGURED YOU LIKE THAT.

25:56.260 --> 25:59.660
ISN'T THAT RIGHT UP
YOUR ALLEY?

25:59.690 --> 26:01.760
NO, NO I DON'T.

26:01.790 --> 26:02.830
WELL, I'M SORRY.
I COULDN'T HELP MYSELF.

26:02.860 --> 26:07.530
JUST HAVE TO STOP BY
AND SEE THAT FACE.

26:07.570 --> 26:09.030
IT'S CUTE, ISN'T IT?

26:09.070 --> 26:10.370
YEAH.

26:10.400 --> 26:12.140
LIKE SEEING IT A LOT MORE
WITH THE BRUISES ALL OVER.

26:13.570 --> 26:15.770
[ LAUGHS EVILLY ]

26:15.810 --> 26:19.240
[ ECHOING ] YEAH IF YOU CAN
SEE YOURSELF. IT'S FUNNY.

26:19.280 --> 26:20.580
YEAH, MAN I LOVE IT.
I LOVE --

26:20.610 --> 26:21.540
YEAH?
YOU CAN'T --

26:21.580 --> 26:24.350
YOU CAN'T HURT ME.

26:24.380 --> 26:26.180
I LOVE THIS SHIT, MAN.
I LOVE IT!

26:26.220 --> 26:28.390
YEAH, WELL,
DON'T YOU WORRY.

26:28.420 --> 26:30.650
THE PAIN IS STILL HERE.

26:30.690 --> 26:32.390
GOOD.

26:32.420 --> 26:34.760
WHERE'S IT AT?
WHERE'S THE PAIN AT?

26:34.790 --> 26:37.390
HERE?

26:37.430 --> 26:41.500
[ SCOFFS ]

26:41.530 --> 26:44.070
WHICH IS A NICE REMINDER
OF WHAT YOU DID TO ME

26:44.100 --> 26:45.770
EVERY TIME I SMILE.

26:45.800 --> 26:47.200
HOPEFULLY,
EVERY TIME YOU SIT.

26:47.240 --> 26:51.340
HMM, YEAH.

26:51.380 --> 26:52.440
THAT WAS BRUTAL.

26:53.410 --> 26:54.410
HELP.
READY?

26:54.450 --> 26:56.150
HELP!
[ ECHOING ] YEAH!

26:56.180 --> 26:57.880
HELP!
JUST SCREAM.

26:57.920 --> 26:59.520
THAT WAS NASTY.

26:59.550 --> 27:01.120
I AIN'T EVEN LIKE THAT
MYSELF.

27:01.150 --> 27:03.120
AFTER THE SHIT YOU DID TO ME,
IT HAD TO BE DONE.

27:03.160 --> 27:06.590
FAIR ENOUGH.

27:06.630 --> 27:08.560
I'M ACTUALLY GLAD
I CAUGHT YOU.

27:08.590 --> 27:09.730
OH, YEAH?

27:09.760 --> 27:12.360
YEAH.

27:12.400 --> 27:15.530
YOU LOOKING AT THIS FACE
OR THIS ASS?

27:15.570 --> 27:17.870
HM?

27:17.900 --> 27:20.600
YOU KNOW WHAT I REALLY
LOVE SEEING THAT FACE.

27:20.640 --> 27:22.470
YOU WERE GASPING FOR AIR
IN THAT PLASTIC BAG.

27:22.510 --> 27:24.440
[ SPEAKING INDISTINCTLY ]

27:24.480 --> 27:27.410
[ GASPING FOR AIR ]

27:30.080 --> 27:32.680
YOU KNOW, I ENJOYED
YOURS IN ONE, TOO.

27:32.720 --> 27:34.550
ALL RIGHT. ENOUGH WITH
THE PLEASANTRIES.

27:34.590 --> 27:36.790
WHAT CAN I DO FOR YOU,
OFFICER?

27:36.820 --> 27:38.520
WHAT'S YOUR GAME?

27:38.560 --> 27:39.690
EXCUSE ME?

27:39.730 --> 27:41.320
YOU HEARD ME.

27:41.360 --> 27:42.730
YOU HAD ME.

27:42.760 --> 27:44.060
YES, I DID.

27:44.100 --> 27:46.930
MM-HMM. AND YOU COULD HAVE
GIVEN ME OVER.

27:46.970 --> 27:48.300
BUT I DIDN'T.

27:48.330 --> 27:51.400
SO THE QUESTION IS...WHY?

27:51.440 --> 27:52.840
BECAUSE I DIDN'T WANT TO.

27:52.870 --> 27:55.640
WHY NOT? WHAT I DID TO YOU
WAS HORRIBLE, MAN.

27:55.670 --> 27:58.010
♪♪

27:58.040 --> 27:59.940
NO, NO, NO, NO, NO.

27:59.980 --> 28:02.110
WHAT YOU DID IS
YOU TURNED ME UP.

28:02.150 --> 28:05.480
YOU KNOW I THOUGHT
I WAS A REAL SICK PUPPY

28:05.520 --> 28:07.420
UNTIL I MET YOU.
OH, COME ON.

28:07.450 --> 28:08.750
DON'T ACT LIKE YOU
WEREN'T AROUSED.

28:08.790 --> 28:12.320
YOU ENJOYED
EVERY MOMENT OF IT.

28:12.360 --> 28:14.560
I'LL GIVE THAT TO YOU.

28:14.590 --> 28:17.630
KILLING IS, UH, LIKE
CLIMAXING TO ME,

28:17.660 --> 28:19.400
WHEN I SEE THE LIFE
LEAVE THEIR EYES.

28:19.430 --> 28:20.600
OH, SO NOW YOU'RE
A SERIAL KILLER, HUH?

28:20.630 --> 28:23.400
NAH. I'M JUST
A LARRY KILLER,

28:23.440 --> 28:27.140
OR SHOULD I SAY
A LADY KILLER?

28:27.170 --> 28:29.410
[ SCOFFS ]
YOU KNOW I CAN SEE THAT.

28:29.440 --> 28:31.140
I BET YOU THE LADIES
LOVE YOU,

28:31.180 --> 28:32.110
THOSE BIG BLUE EYES,

28:32.140 --> 28:35.550
THOSE BIG STRONG MUSCLES.

28:35.580 --> 28:37.710
HM, YEAH, I APPRECIATE
THE FLATTERY.

28:37.750 --> 28:38.880
NEVER HAD A PROBLEM
GETTIN' NONE.

28:38.920 --> 28:39.980
HM.

28:40.020 --> 28:41.380
NOW, WHAT'S YOUR GAME?

28:41.420 --> 28:44.490
SO YOU WANT TO KNOW WHAT TRICKS
I HAVE UP MY SLEEVE, HUH?

28:44.520 --> 28:45.390
I SURE DO.

28:45.420 --> 28:47.660
YOU KNOW, I THINK I PREFER
TO KEEP THAT

28:47.690 --> 28:49.160
FOR THE ELEMENT
OF SURPRISE.

28:49.190 --> 28:50.490
I'MA STAY ON THE READY.

28:50.530 --> 28:51.630
AS YOU SHOULD BE,

28:51.660 --> 28:53.060
BUT TRUST ME,

28:53.100 --> 28:54.660
IT WILL BE GOOD.

28:54.700 --> 28:57.230
IF YOU EVER
COME TO ME AGAIN,

28:57.270 --> 28:59.440
THEY WILL NOT FIND
YOUR REMAINS.

28:59.470 --> 29:01.600
YOU TRYING TO
TURN ME ON?

29:01.640 --> 29:02.940
[ SCOFFS ]

29:02.970 --> 29:06.280
LOOK, WHY DON'T YOU COME BY
MY OFFICE TOMORROW NIGHT?

29:06.310 --> 29:07.140
HELL NO.

29:07.180 --> 29:08.180
OH, COME ON,

29:08.210 --> 29:10.050
I THINK YOU SHOULD COME.
I HAVE, UH...

29:10.080 --> 29:12.920
I HAVE SOME FRIENDS
I WANT YOU TO SAY HI TO.

29:12.950 --> 29:16.320
I'VE MET YOUR FRIENDS BEFORE.
I'LL THINK I'LL PASS.

29:16.350 --> 29:19.360
[ SCOFFS ]
YOU SHOULD COME.

29:19.390 --> 29:21.660
I THINK WE HAVE
MUTUAL ACQUAINTANCES.

29:21.690 --> 29:24.060
WE HAVE NOTHING MUTUAL
OR IN COMMON.

29:24.100 --> 29:27.200
I WILL NOT BE THERE.
OH, COME ON.

29:27.230 --> 29:28.770
PLEASE?

29:28.800 --> 29:30.930
ALRIGHT,
I'LL THINK ABOUT IT.

29:30.970 --> 29:32.840
GREAT.

29:32.870 --> 29:37.110
NOW I HATE TO CUT
THIS MEETING SHORT,

29:37.140 --> 29:41.040
BUT I DO HAVE A PRESS
CONFERENCE TO GET TO.

29:41.080 --> 29:42.280
HM. WELL,
MA'AM...

29:42.310 --> 29:46.050
LET ME GET THE DOOR
FOR YOU.

29:46.080 --> 29:48.990
WAIT, HOW'S MY MAKEUP?

29:49.020 --> 29:50.720
DOESN'T LOOK LIKE
I WHOOPED YOUR ASS.

29:50.760 --> 29:53.490
PERFECT.

29:53.530 --> 29:56.390
♪♪

29:56.430 --> 29:57.860
IS THIS WHERE WE KISS?

29:57.900 --> 29:59.660
THIS IS WHERE YOU TO GET
THE HELL OUT OF MY FACE.

29:59.700 --> 30:02.530
MAYBE NEXT TIME.

30:02.570 --> 30:04.600
♪♪

30:04.640 --> 30:07.440
[ INDISTINCT CONVERSATIONS
IN DISTANCE ]

30:07.470 --> 30:11.110
♪♪

30:11.140 --> 30:13.940
[ SIGHS ]

30:13.980 --> 30:18.280
♪♪

30:18.320 --> 30:20.380
[ SIRENS WAILING ]

30:20.420 --> 30:24.820
♪♪

30:24.860 --> 30:29.330
♪♪

30:29.360 --> 30:33.760
♪♪

30:33.800 --> 30:35.300
♪♪

30:35.330 --> 30:38.600
OH, WHAT HAPPENED?

30:38.640 --> 30:42.110
♪♪

30:42.140 --> 30:44.140
[ RADIO CHATTER ]

30:44.180 --> 30:49.080
♪♪

30:49.110 --> 30:54.020
♪♪

30:54.050 --> 30:58.920
♪♪

30:58.960 --> 31:03.030
♪♪

31:03.060 --> 31:04.590
-MARCIE!
-[ COUGHING ]

31:04.630 --> 31:07.100
-WHAT HAPPENED?!
-HI. UM...

31:07.130 --> 31:08.700
BASTARD ALMOST DIED.

31:08.730 --> 31:09.830
ALEX, YOU OKAY?

31:09.870 --> 31:11.470
YEAH, SHE'LL BE OKAY.

31:11.500 --> 31:13.000
WHAT'S GOING ON?

31:13.040 --> 31:15.170
OH, APPARENTLY SOMEONE, UH,
LOCKED THEM IN THERE

31:15.210 --> 31:17.770
AND SET IT ON FIRE.

31:17.810 --> 31:19.610
IT WAS YOU.

31:19.640 --> 31:21.710
[ SCOFFS ] I DON'T KNOW
WHAT HE'S TALKING ABOUT.

31:21.750 --> 31:25.010
♪♪

31:25.050 --> 31:27.780
ALEX, YOU OKAY?
YOU ALRIGHT?

31:27.820 --> 31:29.950
YOU OKAY?

31:29.990 --> 31:32.420
YEAH, I WILL BE.

31:32.460 --> 31:33.860
LOOK, YOU SHOULD
REALLY GO SEE A DOCTOR.

31:33.890 --> 31:35.690
NO, NO, NO, NO.

31:35.730 --> 31:38.700
-YOU REALLY SHOULD.
-NO, REALLY, I'M OKAY.

31:38.730 --> 31:40.530
I'M FINE.
[ COUGHING ]

31:40.570 --> 31:43.630
ALRIGHT, WELL AT LEAST
TAKE SOME MORE OXYGEN.

31:43.670 --> 31:45.540
THANK YOU.

31:45.570 --> 31:47.700
BENNETT, THANK YOU
FOR SAVING MY LIFE.

31:47.740 --> 31:49.810
DON'T MENTION IT.

31:49.840 --> 31:51.870
I'M SORRY,
WHO THE HELL ARE YOU?

31:51.910 --> 31:54.140
I'M BENNETT.
THAT'S MY WIFE TANYA.

31:54.180 --> 31:56.810
WE JUST MOVED IN
ACROSS THE STREET.

31:56.850 --> 31:58.510
BENNETT?

31:58.550 --> 32:00.320
HI.

32:00.350 --> 32:02.350
YEAH, WELL, UH,
SHE'S FINE, BENNETT.

32:02.390 --> 32:04.620
YOU CAN GET THE HELL
AWAY FROM HER NOW.

32:04.660 --> 32:08.020
ARE YOU TWO MARRIED?

32:08.060 --> 32:09.330
OH, THOSE TWO?
NO, HONEY.

32:09.360 --> 32:12.100
<i> WE</i> WERE MARRIED, AND THEN
HE STARTED SCREWING THAT WHORE

32:12.130 --> 32:13.900
IN THE SHED,
AND THEN, ALL OF A SUDDEN,

32:13.930 --> 32:16.930
THE DOOR'S LOCKED
AND IT'S ON FIRE.

32:16.970 --> 32:18.200
I KNOW YOU DID IT.

32:18.240 --> 32:19.770
-YEAH, OKAY.
-IF IT WASN'T YOU,

32:19.800 --> 32:21.400
IT WAS BRAD.

32:21.440 --> 32:23.670
YOU KNOW I GOT CAMERAS, RIGHT?
I'MA CHECK EM.

32:23.710 --> 32:27.410
WELL, WHEN THE POLICE GET HERE,
WE'LL DO THAT.

32:27.450 --> 32:28.710
YOU'RE A WICKED BITCH.
YOU KNOW THAT?

32:28.750 --> 32:31.080
[ COUGHING ]
ALRIGHT HERE, YOU HAVE
TO BREATHE SOME MORE.

32:31.120 --> 32:33.450
I SAID SHE'S FINE!

32:33.490 --> 32:37.420
♪♪

32:37.460 --> 32:39.490
-WELL, SHE NEEDS --
-HONEY, SHE'S FINE.

32:39.520 --> 32:41.490
LET THE OTHERS TAKE OVER.

32:41.530 --> 32:42.730
OKAY. YEAH. YEAH

32:42.760 --> 32:44.690
BYE.
WELL, IF YOU NEED
ANYTHING --

32:44.730 --> 32:47.560
SHE WON'T BE NEEDING ANYTHING
FROM YOU, PAUL BUNYAN.

32:47.600 --> 32:48.670
THANK YOU.

32:48.700 --> 32:50.030
I'M SORRY, Y'ALL.
I'M NATALIE.

32:50.070 --> 32:51.270
I LIVE OVER ON THE CORNER.

32:51.300 --> 32:54.000
I'M TANYA,
AND THIS IS BENNETT.

32:54.040 --> 32:55.810
SORRY,
SORRY ABOUT ALL THIS.

32:55.840 --> 32:59.680
NO,<i> WE</i> ARE.

32:59.710 --> 33:01.180
WHOO!

33:01.210 --> 33:02.210
-MARCIE.
-HUH?

33:02.250 --> 33:03.680
CAN I TALK TO YOU
FOR A MINUTE?

33:03.720 --> 33:05.450
SURE.

33:05.480 --> 33:07.820
♪♪

33:07.850 --> 33:09.890
[ COUGHING ]

33:09.920 --> 33:11.450
[ RADIO CHATTER ]

33:11.490 --> 33:19.060
[ COUGHING ]

33:19.100 --> 33:23.870
♪♪

33:23.900 --> 33:26.500
[ CELLPHONE BEEPS ]

33:26.540 --> 33:29.940
♪♪

33:29.970 --> 33:32.210
YEAH I NEED TO SPEAK TO LARRY

33:32.240 --> 33:35.180
[ COUGHS ]

33:35.210 --> 33:40.620
UH HUH. YEAH, RANDAL HOLMES.
YOU OUGHT TO KNOW ME BY NOW.

33:40.650 --> 33:44.650
OH, WELL HAVE HIM CALL ME AS
SOON AS HE GETS THIS.

33:44.690 --> 33:46.090
[ COUGHS ]

33:49.530 --> 33:51.930
[ CELLPHONE BEEPS ]

33:58.170 --> 34:02.540
YEAH IT'S ME YOU SON-OF-A-BITCH.
YOU FORGOT I HAD THIS NUMBER?

34:02.570 --> 34:06.110
MM-HMM. YEAH CALL ME AS SOON AS
YOU GET THIS -- AND I MEAN NOW.

34:06.140 --> 34:07.280
WE GOTTA TALK.

34:07.310 --> 34:08.880
I EVEN SIGNED THEM DAMN PAPERS.

34:08.910 --> 34:11.910
YOU TRICKED ME? YOU TRICKED ME
INTO SIGNING THEM DAMN PAPERS?

34:11.950 --> 34:13.180
I GOT SOMETHING FOR YOUR ASS.

34:13.220 --> 34:15.850
CALL ME BACK.

34:15.890 --> 34:17.620
[ CELLPHONE BEEPS ]

34:19.820 --> 34:28.930
[ COUGHING ]

34:28.970 --> 34:30.230
[ CELLPHONE BEEPS ]

34:30.270 --> 34:31.570
[ COUGHS ]

34:33.910 --> 34:38.710
YEAH THIS IS RANDAL HOLMES.
I NEED THE POLICE.

34:38.740 --> 34:42.150
YEAH, YEAH. YEAH SOMEBODY TRIED
TO KILL ME.

34:42.180 --> 34:45.410
BRAD...BRAD MONTGOMERY.
HE LIVES RIGHT NEXT DOOR.

34:45.450 --> 34:49.720
I NEED THE POLICE TO MY HOUSE --
NO, NO, HE'S NOT HERE.

34:49.750 --> 34:51.520
YEAH. I NEED...I NEED THE REAL
POLICE.

34:51.560 --> 34:55.530
DON'T SEND...DON'T SEND LUSHION
MORGAN...OR, OR, OR STEVEN
SIMMONS...

34:55.560 --> 34:58.460
OR BETTER THE HELL NOT SEND
NO DAMN EDDIE.

34:58.500 --> 34:59.700
YEAH SEND EM RIGHT NOW.

34:59.730 --> 35:03.300
OTHERWISE I'M CALLING
THE DAMN FBI...BITCH.

35:03.330 --> 35:04.800
[ CELLPHONE BEEPS ]

35:04.840 --> 35:07.400
[ COUGHS ]

35:07.440 --> 35:09.010
DID YOU LOCK THEM
IN THERE?

35:09.040 --> 35:11.070
[ SCOFFS ]

35:11.110 --> 35:13.480
HE CAN'T PROVE IT.

35:13.510 --> 35:14.610
MARCIE.

35:14.650 --> 35:16.910
WHAT?

35:16.950 --> 35:22.550
YOU DID IT?

35:22.590 --> 35:24.990
I LOST THE BABY,
NATALIE.

35:25.020 --> 35:28.520
[ CRYING ]

35:28.560 --> 35:31.230
THAT SON OF A BITCH MADE
ME LOSE THE BABY AGAIN.

35:31.260 --> 35:33.960
[ SOBBING ]

35:34.000 --> 35:35.060
I'M SO SORRY.

35:35.100 --> 35:36.070
I HATE HIM.

35:36.100 --> 35:37.870
-I'M SO SORRY.
-I HATE HIM SO.

35:37.900 --> 35:38.940
IT'S GONNA BE ALRIGHT.

35:38.970 --> 35:42.000
IT'S NOT GONNA BE ALRIGHT.
HE IS RUINING MY LIFE!

35:42.040 --> 35:44.470
IT'S ALRIGHT.
IT'S ALRIGHT LISTEN.

35:44.510 --> 35:45.580
IT'S ALRIGHT.

35:45.610 --> 35:47.140
YOU COULD'VE KILLED HIM.

35:47.180 --> 35:49.480
WELL, THAT'S WHAT
I CAME HERE TO DO.

35:49.510 --> 35:51.850
I SAW THEM IN THAT SHED...

35:51.880 --> 35:53.150
[ CHUCKLES ]

35:53.180 --> 35:55.450
I JUST WANT HIM
TO LEAVE ME ALONE!

35:55.490 --> 35:57.220
I KNOW, I KNOW,
BUT LISTEN, LISTEN.

35:57.260 --> 35:59.720
KELLY IS ALREADY IN
TROUBLE FOR THAT.

35:59.760 --> 36:01.890
I DON'T CARE.
I DON'T CARE.

36:01.930 --> 36:02.860
-YES, YOU DO.
-I DON'T.

36:02.890 --> 36:04.060
YES, YOU DO.
TRUST ME, YOU DO.

36:04.100 --> 36:05.490
YOU DON'T WANNA GO THROUGH
WHAT SHE'S GOING THROUGH.

36:05.530 --> 36:06.500
TRUST ME YOU DON'T.

36:06.530 --> 36:07.600
-I DON'T?
-YOU DON'T.

36:07.630 --> 36:09.000
[ CHUCKLES NERVOUSLY ]

36:09.030 --> 36:10.230
[ BREATHES DEEPLY ]

36:10.270 --> 36:11.500
NOW STOP IT. OKAY?

36:11.540 --> 36:12.870
STOP.

36:12.900 --> 36:14.640
I NEED YOU TO COME ON,
COME TO MY HOUSE,
AND SIT DOWN, OKAY?

36:14.670 --> 36:17.540
COME ON. COME ON.

36:17.580 --> 36:20.180
[ RADIO CHATTER ]

36:20.210 --> 36:22.680
♪♪

36:22.710 --> 36:25.110
-MARCIE.
-CAN YOU TAKE ME HOME?

36:25.150 --> 36:26.920
-WHAT HAPPENED?
-JUST TAKE ME HOME, PLEASE.

36:26.950 --> 36:27.950
WHAT'S GOING ON?

36:27.990 --> 36:30.120
JUST TAKE HER HOME,
AND GET HER IN THE TUB,

36:30.150 --> 36:33.160
AND GET RID OF THESE CLOTHES
BECAUSE THEY SMELL LIKE GAS.

36:33.190 --> 36:35.660
WHAT DID YOU DO?

36:35.690 --> 36:38.360
SHE -- SHE LOCKED
RANDAL AND ALEX IN A SHED

36:38.400 --> 36:40.400
AND SHE SET IT ON FIRE.

36:40.430 --> 36:42.530
YOU DID WHAT?
YOU'RE KIDDING?

36:42.570 --> 36:43.900
ALRIGHT, COME ON.
YOU NEED TO TAKE HER HOME.

36:43.940 --> 36:45.200
COME ON BEFORE POLICE
GET HERE.

36:45.240 --> 36:47.300
ARE THEY OKAY?

36:47.340 --> 36:49.740
YES, JUST TAKE HER HOME.
TAKE HER HOME NOW.

36:49.770 --> 36:50.670
THEY'RE NOT BURNT,
ARE THEY?

36:50.710 --> 36:51.870
THEY HAVE SOME
SMOKE INHALATION.

36:51.910 --> 36:53.710
THEY'RE GONNA BE FINE.

36:53.750 --> 36:57.410
-BRAD.
-YOU STAY AWAY FROM ME, ALEX.

36:57.450 --> 36:59.820
YOU HEAR ME?
YOU STAY AWAY FROM ME.

36:59.850 --> 37:01.750
BRAD, WAIT, PLEASE,
I'M SO SORRY.

37:01.790 --> 37:03.490
I DON'T CARE WHAT
YOU HAVE TO SAY.

37:03.520 --> 37:06.290
DID YOU TELL RANDAL
THAT MARCIE WAS PREGNANT?

37:06.320 --> 37:07.220
[ Gasping ] BRAD...

37:07.260 --> 37:09.590
-DID YOU?
-YES, YES.

37:09.630 --> 37:13.560
AND THEN YOU WENT BACK INTO
THAT SHED WITH THAT BASTARD?

37:13.600 --> 37:14.760
YES.

37:14.800 --> 37:17.570
OH, WOW, SO YOU CAN
TELL THE TRUTH?

37:17.600 --> 37:19.970
FINALLY.
BRAD?

37:20.000 --> 37:22.000
BRAD...
YOU CAN GO TO HELL, ALEX.

37:22.040 --> 37:23.370
I LOVE YOU, I JUST --

37:23.410 --> 37:24.770
I DON'T CARE WHAT
YOU HAVE TO SAY.

37:24.810 --> 37:27.440
YOU STAY AWAY FROM ME.
YOU HEAR ME?

37:27.480 --> 37:28.810
♪♪

37:28.850 --> 37:31.180
MARCIE, LET'S GO.

37:31.220 --> 37:33.150
♪♪

37:33.180 --> 37:36.850
[ COUGHING ]

37:36.890 --> 37:41.090
[ SNIFFLING ]

37:41.130 --> 37:43.390
[ RADIO CHATTER ]

37:43.430 --> 37:47.500
♪♪

37:47.530 --> 37:51.600
♪♪

37:51.640 --> 37:55.340
[ ENGINE STARTS ]

38:02.910 --> 38:04.380
[ CELLPHONE RINGING ]

38:04.420 --> 38:05.750
[ CELLPHONE BEEPS ]

38:05.780 --> 38:07.950
HEY BABY.

38:07.990 --> 38:09.550
HEY -- I'M JUST ABOUT
TO GET OUTTA HERE.

38:09.590 --> 38:11.850
UM, I NEED TO TELL YOU
SOMETHING.

38:11.890 --> 38:14.360
WHAT IS IT?

38:14.390 --> 38:15.960
[ SIGHS ] SOMEONE LOCKED
ALEX AND RANDAL

38:15.990 --> 38:18.360
INTO THE SHED
AND SET IT ON FIRE.

38:18.400 --> 38:20.530
WHAT?
Yeah.

38:20.570 --> 38:24.170
OH, THAT'S WEIRD CAUSE I DIDN'T
HEAR ANYTHING ON THE RADIO.

38:24.200 --> 38:25.170
Are they okay?

38:25.200 --> 38:27.400
YEAH, NO THEY'RE OKAY.

38:27.440 --> 38:30.010
THIS HAS GOT TO STOP...
AND I MEAN IT.

38:30.040 --> 38:31.910
I KNOW, I KNOW.

38:31.940 --> 38:33.440
Damn.

38:33.480 --> 38:34.740
[ SIGHS ] HOW'S KELLY?

38:34.780 --> 38:36.680
I'M ABOUT TO GO CHECK ON HER
RIGHT NOW.

38:36.710 --> 38:38.310
Okay.

38:38.350 --> 38:40.280
YOU KNOW WHAT...

38:40.320 --> 38:44.090
Do you have a picture of
Justice?

38:44.120 --> 38:46.520
UM, YEAH. I THINK I MAY HAVE ONE
IN MY PHONE.

38:46.560 --> 38:48.320
SEND THAT TO ME.
Okay.

38:48.360 --> 38:51.160
THANKS.

38:51.200 --> 38:52.800
[ CELLPHONE BEEPS ]

38:52.830 --> 38:55.130
UNBELIEVABLE.

38:55.170 --> 39:00.200
♪♪

39:00.240 --> 39:09.980
♪♪

39:10.010 --> 39:18.990
♪♪

39:19.020 --> 39:21.660
LOU LOU.

39:21.690 --> 39:23.030
WHAT'S UP, BABY?

39:23.060 --> 39:24.890
♪♪

39:24.930 --> 39:29.730
SORRY, MAN,
I JUST HEARD THE NEWS.

39:29.770 --> 39:32.840
AND THAT MAKES TWO OF US.

39:32.870 --> 39:36.610
AND THEY'RE DOING JUST FINE.

39:36.640 --> 39:38.140
WHO?

39:38.180 --> 39:41.110
ALEX AND RANDAL.

39:41.150 --> 39:44.250
WHAT HAPPENED TO
THOSE TWO LOSERS?

39:44.280 --> 39:46.320
[ SIGHS ]

39:46.350 --> 39:50.920
♪♪

39:50.960 --> 39:52.120
POURING OUT A LITTLE
SOMETHING FOR THE HOMIE.

39:52.160 --> 39:59.300
OR SHOULD I SAY,
THE HOME-ETTE.

39:59.330 --> 40:01.430
THE HELL ARE YOU
TALKING ABOUT?

40:01.470 --> 40:02.530
[ CHUCKLES ]

40:02.570 --> 40:06.040
WELL, THIS ONE GOOD, LOU.
YOU AIN'T HEARD?

40:06.070 --> 40:08.970
THE HELL ARE YOU
TALKING ABOUT?

40:09.010 --> 40:10.710
KELLY...

40:10.740 --> 40:12.480
IS DEAD.

40:12.510 --> 40:17.680
♪♪

40:18.750 --> 40:19.780
SHE'S DEAD.

40:19.820 --> 40:20.750
AAH! WHOA! WHOA!

40:20.790 --> 40:22.080
YOU ARE SO DISRESPECTFUL.

40:22.120 --> 40:23.320
OH, I'M DISRESPECTFUL.

40:23.350 --> 40:24.650
HEY, RICK?
YEAH?

40:24.690 --> 40:25.720
CAN YOU TAKE A CALL?

40:25.760 --> 40:27.520
<i> NEXT ON,</i>
<i> "IF LOVING YOU IS WRONG"...</i>

40:27.560 --> 40:28.660
SOMEBODY TRIED TO KILL ME.

40:28.690 --> 40:30.390
WELL IT'LL BE YOUR
WORD AGAINST HIS.

40:30.430 --> 40:32.160
-I GOT CAMERAS.
-I KNOW YOU KNOW SOMEONE.

40:32.200 --> 40:33.660
WHAT ARE YOU SAYING?

40:33.700 --> 40:34.860
SOMEONE THAT CAN KILL HIM.

40:34.900 --> 40:36.630
HI THERE.
HI, NICE TO MEET YOU.

40:36.670 --> 40:38.230
LADIES, THIS IS MY WIFE,
TANYA.

40:38.270 --> 40:40.500
SHE IS WATCHING HIM
LIKE A HAWK.

40:40.540 --> 40:41.500
A LITTLE OBSESSIVE
COMPULSIVE I SEE.

40:41.540 --> 40:42.910
KEEPS ON SAYING THAT
SHE NEEDS TO GO HOME.

40:42.940 --> 40:45.840
YOU GET YOUR HANDS
OFF OF ME.

40:45.880 --> 40:48.210
WHAT ARE YOU WEARING?
GET YOUR HAND OFF OF ME!

40:50.080 --> 40:55.080
♪♪

40:57.020 --> 40:59.920
♪♪
